---
layout: layouts/base.njk
permalink: /contact.html
title: Contact
description: Contact Arsalan Iftikhar for career and professional enquiries or NexAura consulting enquiries using the appropriate public route.
canonicalPath: /contact.html
---
<section class="hero">
  <h1>Contact</h1>
  <p>Use the route that best matches the enquiry. Career and professional messages should use the personal email or LinkedIn. Consulting and NexAura enquiries should use the NexAura email route.</p>
</section>

<section class="shell-section" aria-labelledby="career-heading">
  <h2 id="career-heading">{{ contacts.career.label }}</h2>
  <p>For senior BI, data analytics, BI engineering, analytics-engineering or related professional conversations, use the personal email route or LinkedIn.</p>
  <ul class="shell-contact-list">
    <li><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="{{ contacts.career.href }}">{{ contacts.career.email }}</a></li>
    <li><strong>LinkedIn:</strong> <a href="{{ contacts.linkedin.url }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">{{ contacts.linkedin.label }}</a></li>
  </ul>
  <div class="shell-actions">
    <a class="btn" href="{{ cv.url }}" download>{{ cv.label }}</a>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="shell-section" aria-labelledby="consulting-heading">
  <h2 id="consulting-heading">{{ contacts.consulting.label }}</h2>
  <p>For NexAura, consulting, automation or delivery enquiries, use the business email route so the message is kept separate from career conversations.</p>
  <ul class="shell-contact-list">
    <li><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="{{ contacts.consulting.href }}">{{ contacts.consulting.email }}</a></li>
  </ul>
</section>

<section class="cta-card" aria-labelledby="location-heading">
  <h2 id="location-heading">{{ profile.location }}</h2>
  <p>{{ profile.relocation }}. Review the Work page for selected portfolio evidence or use LinkedIn for a professional overview.</p>
  <div class="shell-actions">
    <a class="btn" href="{{ routes.work.url }}">View Work</a>
    <a class="btn" href="{{ contacts.linkedin.url }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">LinkedIn</a>
  </div>
</section>
